<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:define-macro="main"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      i18n:domain="novaideo"
      tal:define="
      su request.static_url;">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" /> 
<body>
        <div style="display: table;
		        	color: #333;
					font-family: Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
					font-size: 14px;
					line-height: 1.42857;
					background-color: #f3f3f3;
					padding-bottom: 15px;">
          <div style="width: 20%;
          	          min-height: 1px;
          	          position: relative;
          	          display: table-cell">
          </div>
          <div style="box-shadow: 0 7px 11px #888888;
					min-height: 1px;
					padding: 15px;
					position: relative;
					width: 50%;
					background-color: white;">
			<div style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 25px">
				<a style="text-decoration: none; color: #777" href="${request.resource_url(request.root, '')}" tal:define="logo getattr(request.root, 'picture', None)">
			        <img tal:condition="logo" src="${logo.url}" class="globe-logo" style=" height: 35px;
																						    margin-top: -12px;
																						    vertical-align: top;">
			        <div tal:omit-tag="" tal:condition="not logo">
			          <img alt="Nova-Ideo" src="${request.static_url('novaideo:static/images/novaideo32.png')}" style=" height: 35px;
																						    margin-top: -12px;
																						    vertical-align: top;"> Nova-Ideo
			        </div>
		        </a>
			</div>
			<div>
                <p>Bonjour ${name},</p>
                <p>
                    Vous verrez ci-dessous les dernières idées et les dernières propositions qui pourraient vous intéresser.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Partagez vos idées! Venez enrichir les propositions des autres.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Venez soutenir les propositions à mettre en application.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>${request.root.title}</strong>, participons pour ensemble faire avancer notre entreprise.
                </p>
            </div>
          	<div tal:repeat="object entities">
			    <a style="text-decoration: none;" tal:attributes="href request.resource_url(object, '@@index')" target="_blank">
			    	<h5 style="font-weight: bold">${object.title} </h5>
			    </a>
			    <div style="color: #333333;
							font-size: 13px;
							padding: 0 10px 5px;">
					${object.presentation_text(200)}
				</div>
			</div>
		  </div>
		  <div style="width: 30%;
		  	          min-height: 1px;
		  	          position: relative;"></div>
		 </div>
  </body>
</html>
